jimjams.airmonitor.sensordata

Class SensorDataGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • jimjams.airmonitor.sensordata.SensorDataGenerator

  • public class SensorDataGenerator
extends Object
    Generates random sensor sensor data to test app. This class uses the singleton pattern and a private constructor. Use getInstance() to access the SensorDataGenerator object.
    Author:
    Sean
